<HEADLINE> 1st add Iraqi Leadership Convenes Urgent Session to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
...the country.
</P>
<P>
Iraqi President Saddam Hussein called on his people and armed
forces to fully mobilize and make all necessary arrangements to
