<HEADLINE> Iran Wins 97-kg Freestyle Wrestling Asiad Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 17 (Xinhua) -- Abass Jadidi of Iran got the
gold medal in the 97-kg freestyle wrestling final at the Asian
Games here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Jadidi outpointed D. Sumuabazar of Mongolia 3-0 to take the top
honour.
</P>
<P>
Soslan Fraev of Uzbekistan outscored Islam Bairamuxov of
Kazakhstan 5-1 to take the bronze medal. 
</P>
