<HEADLINE> S. Korea Takes Wrestling 76-kg Freestyle Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 17 (Xinhua) -- South Korean Moon Eui-Jae took
the gold medal in the 76-kg freestyle wrestling final at the Asian
Games here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Moon outpointed Kenji Koshiba of Japan 10-0 in the title match
to take the top honour, while the Japanese had to settle for a
silver.
</P>
<P>
The bronze medal was won by Ruslan Veliev of Kazakhstan who
defeated Nurbek Izabekov of Kyrgystan 3-2. 
</P>
