points to 1,016.80 and the Second Board Index lost 2.55 points to
171.48.
</P>
<P>
Losers overwhelmed gainers by 584 to 154 while 80 counters were
unchanged, 135 untraded and 43 suspended.
</P>
<P>
The day's total turnover was 277.892 million shares valued at
562.379 million ringgit (about 147.994 million U.S. dollars)
against Wednesday's turnover of 217.701 million shares worth
414.842 million ringgit (about 109.168 million dollars). 
</P>
