Iraq-U.S. conflict as it did in the last confrontation between the
U.S. and Iraq in mid-November.
</P>
<P>
Although sympathizing the Iraq people, the PNA has refrained
from criticizing the U.S., who helped broker the Wye peace deal
between Israel and the Palestinians, in the recent crises in the
Gulf. 
