<HEADLINE> Malaysia to Host Asia Agricultural Convention in 1999 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, December 17 (Xinhua) -- The Asia Agricultural
Exposition and Convention 1999 (AGEX '99) will be held in Malaysia
next year to expose, synergize and accelerate investment and
transfer of technologies and exchange of technical know-how in the
agricultural business in Asia.
</P>
<P>
With the theme "Pushing New Frontiers in Asian Agriculture,
Creating Asia as the Food Powerhouse in the New Millennium", AGEX
'99 to be held from August 26 to August 31 next year was
officially launched here Thursday.
</P>
