<HEADLINE> Gold Medal Not for Sale, Chinese Official </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 17 (Xinhua) -- A Chinese athlete has rebuffed
a bribery attempt from an unidentified person who asked the
Chinese to throw a final in exchange for money.
</P>
<P>
