<HEADLINE> IDB Approves $350 Mln Loan for Colombia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 16 (Xinhua) -- The Inter-American
Development Bank (IDB) Wednesday announced the approval of a 350
million U.S. dollar loan to help modernize electricity sector in
Colombia.
</P>
